## Tmux (Ctrl-a unless otherwise specified, tt for session switch)
Split window horizontally|" / h|h for horizontal
Split window vertically|% / v|v for vertical
Change split orientation|space
Lazygit|g
Maximize current panel|z|z for zoom
Reload .tmux.conf|R|R for reload
Send to all panes on|e|e for echo
Send to all panes off|E|E for echo
Kill session|K|K for kill
Chat with LLM|i|i for intelligence
List windows|w|w for windows
Next window|n / Alt-PgDown|n for next
Previous window|p / Alt-PgUp|p for previous
Move after current win|Ctrl-Alt-PgDown
Move before current win|Ctrl-Alt-PgUp
Clear terminal and buffer|l|l is standard in shell
Scroll up|Ctrl-PgUp
Scroll down|Ctrl-PgDown
Previous window|Ctrl-a twice
Send Ctrl-a when nested|a
Install tmux plugins|I|I for install
Uninstall plugins|alt-u|u for uninstall
Switch panel|
Resize panel 1|Hold C + 
Resize panel 5|Hold M + 
